description: Core project rules for Animal Fantasy World (Unity 6000.4 / C# 9 / URP)
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow the instructions in `AGENTS.md` at the repository root.

Key constraints:
- Unity 6000.4, C# 9.0, .NET Standard 2.1, URP 17.4.0.
- Runtime scripts go in `Assets/Game/Scripts/`, editor scripts in `Assets/Game/Editor/`.
- One class per file, filename matches class name.
- Prefix private fields with `_`. Use `[Header]`, `[Tooltip]`, `[Min]`, `[Range]` on inspector-exposed fields.
- Never edit `.meta`, `.unity`, `.prefab`, or `ProjectSettings/` files directly.
- This is a children's game — keep all content child-safe.
